data.description: Charming remodeled 5 Bedroom 2 bath home with NO HOA features a large living room and an open Kitchen. Recent updates to include new flooring, Fresh interior paint, updated kitchen with granite countertops and all appliances included, updated bathrooms. Plenty of room to add an RV gate that has a pre-existing slab for parking in the oversized backyard. Close to the Cardinals Stadium & Freeways.  Lots of liveable space, and Lots of space for parking up to 6 cars!
